name.k: Loóna - 睡眠更好的幫助，冥想，睡眠追踪器

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 大自然的聲音，入睡音樂，鬧鐘

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: For Loóna, the night time is the right time. Part bedtime story, part interactive activity, and all gorgeous, Loóna winds you down with “sleepscapes,” blends of sound, story, and narration designed to soothe your mind at the end of the day. (Think of them as meditative interactive storybooks, or really easy video games.) Sounds are all breezy forests, babbling rivers, and sweetly buzzing insects; activities involve lighting lanterns or calmly coloring in architectural details. As you progress through sleepscapes, you’ll lose yourself in a fairytale kingdom, explore a dark forest, or simply cozy up to a crackling fire. The app’s developer says the goal is to “recreate this safe bubble from your childhood” and that, if all goes to plan, you’ll shut it down well before you’re finished.
Night time is the right time to wind down with “sleepscapes” – blends of sound, story and calm activities designed to recreate that safe childhood bubble and soothe your mind at the end of the day.

這款幫助睡眠的 App 專為睡前放鬆設計，它獨特的「sleepscapes」內容結合了聲音、故事與靜心活動，為你重現宛如孩提時期的安全感，幫助你在一天結束時歸於寧靜。
